--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

NOTE! The libwim can optionally be linked to the third-party library
"libntfs-3g", which is licensed under the GPL. Usually the GPL is interpreted in
a way that means that any binary that uses a GPL library must be licensed under
the GPL as well, not (for example) the LGPL.

Nevertheless, WimKit use the LGPL option cause does not link at all to the
third-party library "libntfs-3g".
